## Features of this Markdown Previewer:

1. **Beautiful Design**:
   - Gradient background with a clean, modern interface
   - Responsive layout that works on all devices
   - Card-based feature section with hover effects

2. **Full Markdown Support**:
   - Headers (H1-H6)
   - Bold and italic text
   - Inline code
   - Links and images
   - Unordered and ordered lists
   - Blockquotes
   - Code blocks with syntax highlighting
   - Horizontal rules
   - Tables

3. **User-Friendly Interface**:
   - Live editing with real-time preview
   - Clear button to reset the editor
   - Sample button to load example content
   - Copy button to copy the rendered HTML

4. **Responsive Design**:
   - Adapts to different screen sizes
   - Stacked layout on mobile devices

Simply copy and paste this code into an HTML file and open it in any modern browser to start using the Markdown Previewer!
